name: Imprint 1502: Dilaudid
description:
"Imprint" is a variation on "Heartbleed"/"Hush" [1,2]: the background is generated using a stochastic turmite implemented in C++, and the foreground is generated using various tools from the ambient R package. Final image composed in ggplot2.

Sources:

[1] https://art.djnavarro.net/gallery/hush/
[2] https://art.djnavarro.net/gallery/heartbleed/
